          "rawConfiguration": {
            "text": "# ![Velero logo](https://i.imgur.com/Yk8FsuR.png)\n\nThis quickstart was built and tested based on Velero metrics sent to New Relic using Prometheus Agent or Prometheus server. Use the filter dropdowns or search bar to isolate specific backup schedules."
          }
